divs: sighting detailstalking with neighbor in front yard and just glanced up and saw round silver object moving very rapidly toward w\sw. first impression was that this is a ufo as no wings , etc were visible. it was moving in westly direction and then veered to southwestly direction. event lasted @ 20 seconds and lost sight due to tall pine trees. sky is clear and it moved very quickly out of sight. neighbor did not see it. an airliner flew by @ same altitude 30 seconds later and i would estimate at 1\5 the speed of the object. it was exciting to see this object and wished i had had my video camera. i am a former af officer.
Summary: Talking with neighbor and looked up and saw rapidly speeding round silver object.
